narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yeah, you have to take it if you're doing a year long essay.
Definitely take it if you are writing a yearlong. Will help to keep you on track.

A seminar based on presenting revised version of one's senior essay, regardless of the stage. Most students arrive with a large amount of research done already. If you tend to put off work and want to stagger some of your senior essay progress, then this might be a good course; however, there is little accountability until you sign up to present something.
If you are writing a year-long take it! This will help you step back and rethink your essay and actually start writing it.
Great way to start thinking about your senior essay.
Good criticism on senior essay from the professor.
